page.title: 17THE WILD LIFE AT E.C.P
page.content: Eastham Country Park is always full of {Wildlife.}Whether it's Winter,Spring, Summer or Autunm,you'll always see some Wildlife walking,flying or climbing about. During the Winter when most of the trees have lost their leaves and when there are very few flowers to be seen,many people do not concider country parks to be intresting place's to visit.There however,quite a lot of Wildlife present,some{Species}are only found here at this Time of year and can often be seen in the wood's or on the field's around the perimeter of the wood's.
